rComments: The best prof I've meet in UTM.

Honestly one of the best professors I've had. took eco209 with him, he is very concerned with students learning and makes sure you understand the concepts. He is willing to reteach  a good portion of the lecture again in Office hours if need be.
Hard to understand at first with his accent, but you get used to it.  First test was hard, but the rest were fine if you studied for them.  Will be there for you if you have questions.
